items.longDescription: <br><b>Refurbished Samsung Galaxy Tab 4 With Wi-Fi 7.0" Touchscreen Tablet PC:</b><br><b>Technical specifications:</b><ul><li>1.2GHz quad-core processor</li><li>1.5GB DDR2 of system memory</li><li>7.0" touchscreen, 1280 x 800 resolution</li><li>Built-in 802.11a/b/g/n WiFi and bluetooth v4.0</li></ul><b>Additional Features:</b><ul><li>Back 3MP webcam and front 1.3MP webcam</li><li>Quad-core tablet has microUSB 2.0 port</li><li>8GB onboard storage memory, additional memory via microSD card slot</li><li>Built-in speakers</li><li>GPS with GLONASS</li><li>Rechargeable lithium-ion battery</li><li>Weighs 1.6 lbs; 10.75" x 0.62" x 6.97" dimensions</li></ul><b>Software and Applications:</b><ul><li>Android 4.4 OS (KitKat)</li><li>WatchON, Netflix, alarm, email, s-voice, Samsung apps</li><li>Hancom office viewer, s-browser</li><li>Media formats: MP4, 3GP, WMV, ASF, AVI, FLV, MKV, WEBM, M4A, MP3, 3GA, AAC, OGG, WAV, WMA, FLAC, BMP, GIF, JPEG, ICO, SVG-T</li></ul><b>What's in the box:</b><ul><li>Refurbished tablet, battery and AC adapter</li></ul><br><b>What's a Tablet PC?</b><br>Tablet PCs are compact, ultra-portable entertainment devices that let you read email, surf the internet, read ebooks, view photos, play games, listen to music and watch video files. Most tablets are based on a smaller operating system, which allows you to purchase and download additional applications from supported stores. Tablet PCs do not have a CD/DVD drive and will not run Microsoft Windows or its applications. Tablet PCs function as a secondary device for casual entertainment purposes, and are not meant to replace a computer. They are ideal for use around the home and on the go with WiFi or 3-4G mobile broadband connections (pay as you go, contract may be required for service).
